aim_dustsiege            by Murf
-----------------            ----------

This is a DUST based map. Ts start with AK47s and CTs with M4A1s (plus secondary weapons). Pretty fun map in my opinion when i played with some friends. This map is pretty simple, so much so it was made in 2 days (or even less).

Uses standard textures and standard everything.

Please assess!
Have fun! :)

By Murf
